{"tid":1871932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尋找03年沙士患者同醫護人員","createTime":"2020-02-09T19:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T01:17:17.000Z","uid":348643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75e44ab8bf7117eb3d0e0fa4f4e12e3350c5c1d6","tid":1871932,"uid":348643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:02:38.000Z","msg":"你好，我是某間媒體機構的記者。<br />\n<br />\n政府對於新型冠狀病毒採取的防疫措施不夠到位，引起市民的恐慌，包括排隊買口罩，醫護人員罷工呼籲政府全面封關。<br />\n<br />\n2003年沙士給香港帶來了巨大的重創，有不少醫護人員在前線對抗沙士感染，淘大花園也發生了大規模的社區爆發。雖然有不少患者最後康復，但他們逃不過的是牽連一輩子的後遺症。<br />\n<br />\n我們不希望的事情重複蹈轍，所以我們希望通過這些患者和醫護人員的經歷，反應市民大眾的聲音，使政府能夠做出有效及時的防疫措施。因此我們希望做一個深度報導，如有你有認識的患者和醫護人員，請聯繫我們，我們會應受訪者要求保護他的隱私，十分感謝！"},{"pid":"fd710d8f0af7a37981f96a4a46f45e8e0944ac86","tid":1871932,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:04:03.000Z","msg":"某？"},{"pid":"0d9dc6d970d670c84d572bfa5a2948a28622fde0","tid":1871932,"uid":348643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd710d8f0af7a37981f96a4a46f45e8e0944ac86","tid":1871932,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:04:03.000Z","msg":"某？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:04:24.000Z","msg":"我係學生記者"},{"pid":"10af5c86940e7ed7444f450d29146cf5927ddcea","tid":1871932,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hvcagbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvcagbp.jpg&h=1e272efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6B2RJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6B2RJ4.jpg&h=2604c676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StbN2PD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStbN2PD.jpg&h=874d5396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MikryXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMikryXq.jpg&h=76391cc2